Rango is a pet chameleon always on the lookout for action and 
adventure, except the fake kind, where he directs it and acts in it. 
After a car accident, he winds up in an old western town called 
Dirt. What this town needs the most is water, but they also need 
a hero and a sheriff. The thirsty Rango instantly takes on the 
role of both and selfishly agrees to take on the case of their 
missing water.
